                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Survival."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " You can't win if you're dead. Live to fight another day - when the odds might be more in your favor. (Any)"
