                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Victory."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Winning is the real measure of a person. In the end, the only thing that matters is the scoreboard. (Evil)"
                  }
